      <talk_question mid="86"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Heraldry Scholar Bailey</FONT> knows many things.<BR>It would be a good idea to ask him for some advice.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-accepting-acceptted" mid="88"><![CDATA[<html>(Ask about the Pendant of the Pure.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey${action:Talk}<BR>Ah, you are <FONT color=#387206>{user_class} {user_nick}</FONT>!<BR>How are you feeling? You don't look very well…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300030">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-a" mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>Alright.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey${action:Talk}<BR>The <FONT color=#a82424>Pendant of the Pure</FONT>, eh? I remember Cleric William owned one. Try asking his disciple, Master Cleric Jermain.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-a" image="QW_16.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-b" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>(Ask about the ancient relic.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>The <FONT color=#a82424>Pendant of the Pure</FONT>…? The Black Knight seems to be greatly interested in <FONT color=#a82424>ancient relics</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-1-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n028_scholar_bailey-2" mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR>Ancient relics are treasures left behind by the Ancients, the people who served the Goddess long ago.<BR>Under the blessing of the Goddess, they acquired deep knowledge about <FONT color=#a82424>heraldry</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>jewels</FONT>, but they disappeared into history due to unknown reasons. All that is left about them are their relics.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-1" image="QN_Npc_Scholar_Baily.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Heraldry Scholar Bailey</FONT> knows many things.<BR>It would be a good idea to ask him for some advice.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n028_scholar_bailey-2" image="QN_Npc_Cl_master_Germain.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Master Cleric Jermain</FONT> was a disciple of Priest William. He should be able to help you with the details of that pendant.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>Do you happen to have the Pendant of the Pure with you?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Hello there.<BR>I'm worried about the <FONT color=#a82424>Prophet</FONT>. She must be terrified with the Black Knight.<BR>We have to save her as soon as possible…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-a" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300030">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-b" mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>Where is William right now?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>The Pendant of the Pure? That's what my master, <FONT color=#a82424>Master Cleric William</FONT> always carried with him...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-b" image="QW_17.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-c" mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain${action:Talk}<BR>My master… He took part in the Monster Struggle to fight the monsters in <FONT color=#a82424>Forest of Death</FONT> long time ago… and he was martyred there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-c" image="QW_17.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-d" mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>I see. I will look for it at the Forest of Death myself.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>The Forest of Death was engulfed with a poisonous cloud during that time. Due to that, I wasn't able to recover my master's body...<BR>The poison cloud even turned some of the fallen into ghouls...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-2-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-3" mid="65"><![CDATA[<html>Alright.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="64"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I should have recovered his remains...<BR>When you're there, could you bring his remains back too?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-3" image="QW_17.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Thank you...the <FONT color=#a82424>Pendant of the Pure</FONT> should still be on him if you find his remains in the <FONT color=#a82424>Forest of Death</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300030">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-a" mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>(You tell him about what happened in the Forest of Death.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Did you find his remains and the <FONT color=#a82424>Pendant of the Pure</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-a" image="QM_GhoulBlue.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-b" mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>The monster refused to let it go...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>What...?<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Ghoul Baldness</FONT> was wearing the <FONT color=#a82424>Pendant of the Pure</FONT>? How is that possible? Are you saying that monster messed with my master's remains and stole it from him?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-c" mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Ahh… ah… master…<BR>(Jermain is sobbing)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-d" mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>Are you saying that the blue ghoul was William?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>(Jermain continues weeping.)<BR>Master... how could it be... how could you be wandering the earth as the undead...even after your sacrifice...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-d" image="QM_GhoulBlue.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-e" mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>I see… I'm sorry.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>I guess that's the only way a ghoul could wear the holy <FONT color=#a82424>Pendant of the Pure</FONT>.<BR>Though he had become an undead, his deep faith must have protected him from being destroyed by the holy powers.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-f" mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain${action:Talk}<BR>I'm okay now...<BR>He must be by the Goddess's side in peace now...<BR>(He turns to the skies and shouts) Master, please rest in peace…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-f" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-g" mid="46"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#a94407>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-g" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-h" mid="83"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="82"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>We still have to figure out how this happened. Sometimes, great bitterness and regret may cause the dead to continue wandering the earth...however, for a cleric...it is unheard of. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-h" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-4-!next" mid="85"><![CDATA[<html>(Jermain looks desperate)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="84"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Clearly, some corrupted monsters or mad magicians had something to do with this.<BR>We must find the ones behind this, and punish them for their insolence!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n034_cleric_master_germain-5" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-5-a" mid="78"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="74"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>We still have to figure out how this happened. Sometimes, great bitterness and regret may cause the dead to continue wandering the earth...however, for a cleric...it is unheard of. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
