      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-5-!next" mid="80"><![CDATA[<html>Uh-huh.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="79"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Jermain$<BR>Clearly, some corrupted monsters or mad magicians had something to do with this.<BR>We must find the ones behind this, and punish them for their insolence!</html>]]></talk_question>
